channel.title: Graha Mulia Jaya
channel.description: We are a leading distributor of AHU (Air Handling Unit) systems, recognized as the first to successfully upgrade an air handling unit in a toothpaste factory in Surabaya. By transitioning the motor from IE1 to IE5 and implementing our Danfoss system, we achieved nearly 80% reduction in load, showcasing our expertise in delivering innovative and energy-efficient solutions.
